{"tid":998105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"相守70年…夫妻病床牽手一同離世　女兒撰文紀念父母愛情","createTime":"2019-01-27T16:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T17:54:19.000Z","uid":212399,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c203c6206ea86cb4d5daa694c1c990315f7dd9a2","tid":998105,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n澳洲這對夫婦的感情令人動容！他們一生相守直到生命的最後一刻都陪伴在彼此身邊，結婚70年的他們最後在療養院的病房內，牽著對方的手一同離開這個世界，最讓人感到不可思議的是，就連醫生也不能判斷究竟是誰先過世，因此夫妻的死亡時間是一樣的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/27/1756731-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F1756731-XXL.jpg&h=51fdadf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲老夫妻重病時是住在同一間病房內。（圖／翻攝自dailymail）<br />\n這段相伴一生的故事，是由擔任記者的女兒Amanda撰稿在英國《每日郵報》，92歲的弗朗西斯（Francis Ernest Platell）和90歲的諾瑪（Norma June Platell），在1月6日當天一同過世。<br />\nAmanda表示爸媽在療養院是共用一個房間，床就在隔壁伸出手就能牽到對方，這天因為媽媽的呼吸異常而爸爸的情況也不穩定，因此護理師不斷進出病房查看，不料只間隔了短短10分鐘，夫妻兩人都已經自然離世，時間相當接近醫生也沒辦法判斷誰先離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/27/1756732-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F1756732-XXL.jpg&h=26637f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Francis（左）和Norma（中）已經結婚70年。（圖／翻攝自dailymail）<br />\n其實早在3年前醫生就直言，媽媽Norma無法撐過當年的聖誕節，Norma患有阿茲海默症且情況日益嚴重，連話都說不出來，Amanda回憶她聽到媽媽說出的最後一句話是「My husband（我的丈夫）」，雖然媽媽撐過了聖誕節，但卻已經失去了所有生活能力，不過即使如此，爸爸仍堅持每日親自幫妻子清洗、餵食，直到後來體力無法負荷才不得已送進療養院。<br />\nAmanda想起爸爸曾說過「有媽媽的地方就是家」，媽媽住院期間爸爸每天風雨無阻的到療養院陪伴，兩人一起吃午餐、牽手看電視，然而年事已高的他在經歷摔倒和輕微中風後也住進療養院，夫妻倆同一間房、床靠著床，就這樣一直待在一起，直到今年1月6日一同離開人世。（整理：實習編輯黃韻璇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=491557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D491557&d=J70CgiO6Bt2FN2ifhVeqm8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=7170bb1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D491557&h=7c5c6693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=491557</a>"},{"pid":"75db179a11c0010fca3d39a0abca4bb0943f3e86","tid":998105,"uid":64601,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"其實幾幸福，希望佢哋可以相愛到下個世紀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49091d5e3bf2800d7f14ce4e372d951385cce904","tid":998105,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b40d18ed1edbdc2f495d199bc4544eb9a7a1e2","tid":998105,"uid":20552,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望佢哋下一世都繼續做夫妻"},{"pid":"b0096fd9f371a05c76b60241915cdc580b926f57","tid":998105,"uid":55511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"有媽媽的地方就是家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此心安處便是吾鄉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5766d59358c4fdfda7e58b69161a324e5011e6a1","tid":998105,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa629aac68ef843678ed36359493cac89cda80f","tid":998105,"uid":150858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:58:23.000Z","msg":"一齊去世，可能掛住對方既，只係幾分鐘⋯⋯<br />\n之後就一齊上路喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔需要某一方一直牽掛⋯⋯"},{"pid":"4aee5baafafadc57fb00956e5af895002638edcd","tid":998105,"uid":33410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac